@startuml

title Diagrama de Secuencia: UVL → BDD + Árbol de Features al Frontend

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam roundcorner 5

participant "Django\n(apps.py)" as Django
participant "FlamapyService" as Flamapy
database "agroTrain.uvl" as UVL
participant "BDD\n(PyBDD)" as BDD
participant "Frontend\n(React)" as Frontend

== Inicialización del Servidor ==

Django -> Flamapy : warm_up(UVL_MODEL_PATH)
activate Flamapy

Flamapy -> UVL : leer fichero UVL
activate UVL
UVL --> Flamapy : árbol de features (texto UVL)
deactivate UVL

Flamapy -> BDD : construir BDD desde árbol UVL\n(Flamapy + PySAT)
activate BDD
BDD --> Flamapy : BDD compilada
deactivate BDD
note right of Flamapy : BDD almacenada\na nivel de clase

Flamapy -> Flamapy : recopilar etiquetas\n(atributo "label" de cada nodo)

Flamapy -> Flamapy : derivar ámbitos por paso\n(atributo "wizard_step" de subárboles)\n→ _scope_features: dict[step → features]

Flamapy --> Django : warm_up() completado
deactivate Flamapy

note over Django, Flamapy : Servidor listo. BDD en caché.

== Solicitud del Feature Model ==

Frontend -> Flamapy : GET /api/v1/configurator/feature-model
activate Flamapy

Flamapy -> Flamapy : to_dict()\nserializar árbol recursivamente

note right of Flamapy
  Estructura FeatureModelNode:
  - name
  - relations (tipo: MANDATORY /
    OPTIONAL / ALTERNATIVE / OR)
  - attributes (label, wizard_step,
    csv_col, window_size, ...)
  - constraints (AST)
end note

Flamapy --> Frontend : 200 OK — JSON (árbol completo + restricciones)
deactivate Flamapy

Frontend -> Frontend : almacenar en caché\n(React Query)
Frontend -> Frontend : renderizar wizard\n(paso 0 — Parcela)

@enduml
